l)\n        required: true\n        type: string\n      issue_number:\n        description: Issue number to work on\n        required: true\n        type: string\n\npermissions:\n  contents: write\n  pull-requests: write\n  issues: write\n\njobs:\n  run:\n    uses: Clockwork-Pilot/autopilot/.github/workflows/coding-agent.yml@main\n    with:\n      runner_label:     ${{ inputs.runner_label }}\n      issue_number:     ${{ inputs.issue_number }}\n      cache_key_prefix: ${{ github.repository }}-agent-img\n    secrets:\n      UPSTREAM_PR_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.UPSTREAM_PR_TOKEN }}\n", "userModified": false}, "tool_use_id": "toolu_0188ggnJ9go4W7Mn4DzjTTdt", "duration_ms": 15}}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-24T15:48:37.239075", "event": "Write", "data": {"session_id": "b6280e45-69a0-4be3-81ec-a2d05890506f", "transcript_path": "/home/node/.claude/projects/-workspace/b6280e45-69a0-4be3-81ec-a2d05890506f.jsonl", "cwd": "/workspace", "permission_mode": "bypassPermissions", "hook_event_name": "PreToolUse", "tool_name": "Write", "tool_input": {"file_path": "/workspace/.github/workflows/agent-with-dockerfile.yml", "content": "name: Agent (with Dockerfile)\n\n# Consumer caller: exercises the `dockerfile` input path. The image is built\n# once in the `image` job (ensure-docker-image.yml on the self-hosted runner)\n# and its local tag is handed to coding-agent.yml via docker_image. The\n# dockerfile + build_args + cache_key_prefix are declared only here \u2014 the\n# downstream reusable workflow does not re-derive them.\n#\n# Like agent.yml, this is workflow_dispatch only \u2014 running it requires a\n# self-hosted runner labeled with your GitHub username and an issue number.\n\non:\n  workflow_dispatch:\n    inputs:\n      runner_label:\n        description: GitHub username (matches self-hosted runner label)\n        required: true\n        type: string\n      issue_number:\n        description: Issue number to work on\n        required: true\n        type: string\n\npermissions:\n  contents: write\n  pull-requests: write\n  issues: write\n\njobs:\n  image:\n    uses: Clockwork-Pilot/autopilot/.github/workflows/ensure-docker-image.yml@main\n    with:\n      runner_label:     ${{ inputs.runner_label }}\n      base_image:       ghcr.io/clockwork-pilot/autopilot-ws:latest\n      dockerfile:       Dockerfile.agent-sample\n      tag:              autopilot-agent\n      cache_key_prefix: ${{ github.repository }}-agent-img\n\n  run:\n    needs: image\n    uses: Clockwork-Pilot/autopilot/.github/workflows/coding-agent.yml@main\n    with:\n      runner_label: ${{ inputs.runner_label }}\n      issue_number: ${{ inputs.issue_number }}\n      docker_image: ${{ needs.image.outputs.docker_image }}\n    secrets:\n      UPSTREAM_PR_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.UPSTREAM_PR_TOKEN }}\n"}, "tool_use_id": "toolu_015Bjoj4RAtJCfdHTq4VdtzJ"}}
