{"timestamp": "2026-04-25T21:02:18.881658", "event": "Stop", "status": "allowed", "data": {"session_id": "c966cf96-0585-4339-a113-e99e77a184d4", "transcript_path": "/home/node/.claude/projects/-workspace/c966cf96-0585-4339-a113-e99e77a184d4.jsonl", "cwd": "/workspace/autopilot", "permission_mode": "bypassPermissions", "hook_event_name": "Stop", "stop_hook_active": false, "last_assistant_message": "Five lines of proof, three angles:\n\n**1. Test-target wiring (action.yml is loaded, not bypassed)**\n\nBoth wrapper jobs in `act-step-runner.yml` consist of exactly one step: `uses: ./.github/actions/<name>` with a `with:` block. No `run: bash \u2026script.sh`. The dispatcher's Path A (composite) loads `action.yml` via `yq '.' \"$ACTION_YML\"` (gate at line 81 of `act-step-dispatch.sh`) and walks `runs.steps[]` from there.\n\n**2. Fixture coverage**\n\n- `parse-issue`: 4 cases (`frontmatter-branches`, `full`, `no-frontmatter`, `slug-cap`).\n- `choose-branch`: 1 case (`default`).\n\nEach case has `input.json` (drives the with: expressions) and `expected.json` (asserts on `$GITHUB_OUTPUT` parsed to JSON). All 5 ran green just now.\n\n**3. Negative proof \u2014 earlier in this session**\n\nWhen I temporarily reverted the `parse-issue/action.yml:16` description fix, the suite failed with:\n```\nyq: ParserError: ... line 16, column 25: did not find expected ',' or '}'\nFAIL: parse-issue/{frontmatter-branches,full,no-frontmatter,slug-cap} (dispatch)\n```\nThat's the gate firing \u2014 if the harness still bypassed `action.yml`, the suite would have stayed green. After restoring the fix, all 4 went back to OK. Same gate applies to `choose-branch` (Path A is shared).\n\n**Constraints locking it in (verified, fails_count=1, cmd immutable):**\n\n| Constraint | Guards |\n|---|---|\n| `parse_issue_test_uses_composite_action` | wrapper must `uses: ./.github/actions/parse-issue` |\n| `choose_branch_test_uses_composite_action` | wrapper must `uses: ./.github/actions/choose-branch` |\n| `composite_actions_yaml_loadable` | `act-step-dispatch.sh` must load action.yml via yq |\n| `parse_issue_via_action` | parse-issue fixtures must pass end-to-end |\n| `choose_branch_via_action` | choose-branch fixtures must pass end-to-end |\n| `actionlint_passes` | both action.yml files lint clean |\n\nIf anyone reverts a wrapper to `run: bash \u2026script.sh`, constraint #1 or #2 fails. If anyone mutates `act-step-dispatch.sh` to skip `action.yml`, constraint #3 fails. If anyone breaks an action.yml, constraints #4/#5/#6 fail. The three-way drift between action.yml \u2194 script.sh \u2194 fixtures is now structurally pinned."}, "vars": {"PROJECT_ROOT": "/workspace", "PLUGIN_ROOT": "/plugin", "WORKSPACE_ROOT": "/workspace"}}
