{"timestamp": "2026-04-25T23:49:10.247316", "event": "UserPromptSubmit", "data": {"session_id": "c966cf96-0585-4339-a113-e99e77a184d4", "transcript_path": "/home/node/.claude/projects/-workspace/c966cf96-0585-4339-a113-e99e77a184d4.jsonl", "cwd": "/workspace", "permission_mode": "bypassPermissions", "hook_event_name": "UserPromptSubmit", "prompt": "composite action                                                                                                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  One new file in autopilot:                                                                                                                                            \n  .github/actions/run-claude-agent/action.yml\n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  name: run-claude-agent\n  description: Run the Claude agent (or its post-run commit pass) inside the autopilot-ws docker image.                                                                 \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  inputs:\n    model:                                                                                                                                                              \n      description: Anthropic model ID. Required.\n      required: true                                                                                                                                                    \n    prompt:\n      description: Prompt fed to claude -p. Required.                                                                                                                   \n      required: true\n    agent_image:                                                                                                                                                        \n      description: Local docker tag prepared by ensure-docker-image. Required.\n      required: true                                                                                                                                                    \n    timeout_secs: \n      description: Hard timeout for the docker run.                                                                                                                     \n      required: false\n      default: \"180\"                                                                                                                                                    \n    extra_docker_args:\n      description: Extra args spliced into `docker run` (forwarded as CLAUDE_EXTRA_DOCKER_ARGS).                                                                        \n      required: false                                                                                                                                                   \n      default: \"\"                                                                                                                                                       \n    allow_git_commit:                                                                                                                                                   \n      description: When \"true\", passes --allow-git-commit (skip proxy, allow commits).                                                                                  \n      required: false                                                                                                                                                   \n      default: \"false\"                                                                                                                                                  \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  runs:           \n    using: composite\n    steps:\n      - shell: bash\n        env:                                                                                                                                                            \n          MODEL:                    ${{ inputs.model }}\n          PROMPT:                   ${{ inputs.prompt }}                                                                                                                \n          AGENT_IMAGE:              ${{ inputs.agent_image }}                                                                                                           \n          TIMEOUT_SECS:             ${{ inputs.timeout_secs }}\n          CLAUDE_EXTRA_DOCKER_ARGS: ${{ inputs.extra_docker_args }}                                                                                                     \n          ALLOW_GIT_COMMIT:         ${{ inputs.allow_git_commit }}                                                                                                      \n        run: |                                                                                                                                                          \n          flag=()                                                                                                                                                       \n          [ \"$ALLOW_GIT_COMMIT\" = \"true\" ] && flag=(--allow-git-commit)                                                                                                 \n          bash \"$GITHUB_ACTION_PATH/../../scripts/run-in-docker-claude.sh\" \"${flag[@]}\"                                                                                 \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  $GITHUB_ACTION_PATH is set automatically by GitHub when running a composite action; it points at the autopilot checkout's .github/actions/run-claude-agent/. So       \n  $GITHUB_ACTION_PATH/../../scripts/run-in-docker-claude.sh resolves to autopilot's .github/scripts/run-in-docker-claude.sh \u2014 same trick check-constraints uses.        \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  Three call-site changes in coding-agent.yml (run-agent job):                                                                                                          \n   \n  Before (3 places):                                                                                                                                                    \n  - name: Run Claude agent in Docker\n    id: agent                       \n    env:                                                                                                                                                                \n      MODEL:        ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.model }}\n      TIMEOUT_SECS: ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.timeout_secs }}                                                                                                       \n      PROMPT:       ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.agent_task_text }}                                                                                                    \n      AGENT_IMAGE:  ${{ inputs.docker_image }}                      \n      CLAUDE_EXTRA_DOCKER_ARGS: ${{ inputs.extra_docker_args }}                                                                                                         \n    run: |                                                                                                                                                              \n      echo \"::group::Claude Agent Output\"                                                                                                                               \n      set +e                                                                                                                                                            \n      bash .github/scripts/run-in-docker-claude.sh                                                                                                                      \n      EXIT_CODE=$?                                                                                                                                                      \n      echo \"::endgroup::\"\n      echo \"exit_code=$EXIT_CODE\" >> \"$GITHUB_OUTPUT\"                                                                                                                   \n      exit \"$EXIT_CODE\"                                                                                                                                                 \n   \n  After:                                                                                                                                                                \n  - name: Run Claude agent in Docker\n    id: agent                                                                                                                                                           \n    uses: Clockwork-Pilot/autopilot/.github/actions/run-claude-agent@main\n    with:                                                                \n      model:             ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.model }}                                                                                                         \n      prompt:            ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.agent_task_text }}\n      agent_image:       ${{ inputs.docker_image }}                                                                                                                     \n      timeout_secs:      ${{ needs.parse-issue.outputs.timeout_secs }}\n      extra_docker_args: ${{ inputs.extra_docker_args }}                                                                                                                \n                                                        \n  The set +e ... exit \"$EXIT_CODE\" dance becomes the action's natural exit code \u2014 composite actions propagate the inner step's exit code. To still emit exit_code as a  \n  step output for the gate on Agent commit, the composite's run can still write to $GITHUB_OUTPUT. (Slightly subtle: composite-action outputs need to be declared in    \n  outputs: and referenced via steps.<id>.outputs.<x>. Easy to do.)                                                                                                      \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  Same shape for the agent-commit step (with allow_git_commit: true) and for the constraint step (separate composite, since it calls a different script).               \n   \n  Net effect:                                                                                                                                                           \n  - coding-agent.yml's run-agent job no longer references bash .github/scripts/... at all. It calls only composite actions, all of whose paths are resolved by GitHub.\n  - The script run-in-docker-claude.sh keeps living in autopilot's .github/scripts/ \u2014 just its caller becomes a composite action.                                       \n  - No second checkout, no path tricks in the workflow, no inline shell.                                                         \n  - Pattern matches check-constraints exactly.                                                                                                                          \n                                                                                                                                                                        \n  Locking it in: add a constraint analogous to the harness ones (coding_agent_uses_run_claude_agent_action) that asserts the run-agent job invokes the composite via    \n  uses: and forbids the bare bash .github/scripts/... form. Same regression-prevention discipline you already have for the parse-issue/choose-branch tests.             \n "}}
